== Then and now ==

In TTD, multiplayer wasn't stable, it was hard to get working, and, with the patch, you couldn't transfer keystrokes, and there could only be 2 competing players. Thus, there was no good way to play a decent multiplayer game with you're friends.

Now, multiplayer is as good as stable, quite easy to get working, and everything can be transferred. Also, there are big map versions out, so you don't get cramped with you're competitors. Also, there is some new feautures; up to 8 players and cooperative gameplay.

== The command line way ==

In the [[en/Manual/Command line]], you can use the following options:

